  <accessibilityDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Accessible rooms are available on request, please call to book.</li>
<li>The reception hall, breakfast room and restaurant are all located on the ground floor, but there are seven steps to reach the first level where there is a lift. There are five steps down to the beach. As a result, this hotel may not be suitable for guests with accessibility requirements.</li>
</ul>]]></accessibilityDescription>
