  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A buffet breakfast is served between 8am – 10.30am and offers sweet and savoury options including bread, brioche, croissants, yogurts, cereals and cakes. If you choose half board or full board you'll dine at the Altrove Bistrot &amp; Wine Bar. You can also upgrade to half board at Restaurant Baia del Silenzio.</p>
<p><strong>Restaurant Baia del Silenzio</strong> features in the Michelin Guide and offers a lovely setting for an elegant meal, overlooking the beautiful Bay of Silence. The Chef prepares Ligurian cuisine using seasonal produce, classically prepared cuts of meat and fresh fish specials.</p>
<p><strong>Altrove</strong> <strong>Bistrot &amp; Wine Bar</strong> is a stylish spot where you’ll find an extensive wine list. Choose from the best known, Italian, French and international wines or try one of the carefully selected bottles from small, regional vineyards. They also serve delicious cuisine here that can be enjoyed in the bar or outside on the terrace with sea views.</p>
<p><strong>Karma</strong> <strong>Lounge Bar </strong>overlooks the sea and offers a wide choice of drinks, from coffee in the morning to cocktails later on. If you're peckish, they also serve a selection of snacks.</p>
<div class="js-show-description-text"></div>]]></cateringDescription>
